name: Mace Windu, Jedi Master (AI)
Lore: 'Jedi Council member who is known to be one of the strongest members of the Council. Has come to Naboo to investigate the death of the mysterious ''dark warrior.''',
Text: 'Deploys -2 on Naboo. While on Naboo, once during your control phase may use 1 Force to cancel Maul''s immunity to attrition for remainder of turn. Immune to attrition < 3 (< 5 while on Naboo).',
